## Summary

This documentation covers the Amplitude Experiment JavaScript SDK for client-side feature flag evaluation, including installation via npm/yarn/script, initialization with Amplitude Analytics or third-party providers, remote and local evaluation methods, variant fetching and caching, automatic exposure tracking, and integrations with analytics SDKs.

